<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:Vukovar_water_tank.jpg" class="image" title="Vukovar water tank.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4b/Vukovar_water_tank.jpg/300px-Vukovar_water_tank.jpg" width="300" height="450" border="0" /></a><br />
The water tower in Vukovar, 2005. Heavily damaged in the <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Vukovar" title="Battle of Vukovar">battle</a>, the tower has been preserved as a symbol of the town's suffering.</td>
